OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,FIn an election year for one island and
OL,7,Fanother on the way for the next, women
OL,8,Facross the Channel Islands are being
OL,9,Furged to consider a career in politics.
OL,11,F'Women in Public Life' in Guernsey and
OL,12,F'vote.je' in Jersey both say the
OL,13,Fpresence of female deputies is
OL,14,Fessential for the proper functioning
OL,15,Fof a representative democracy.
OL,17,FTheir campaigns hope to inspire women
OL,18,Finto public office to create greater
OL,19,Fgender equality.
