OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,FIn Guernsey, only eight deputies - 25%
OL,7,Fof all elected States Members - are
OL,8,Fcurrently women.
OL,10,FWomen in Public Life has run a series
OL,11,Fof political training workshops for
OL,12,Fwomen to change that ahead of June's
OL,13,Felection.
OL,15,FSupported by current female deputies,
OL,16,Fthe workshops aim to equip women with
OL,17,Fthe practical skills they need to run
OL,18,Fa successful political campaign - for
OL,19,Fexample, manifesto writing, door-
OL,20,Fknocking, and networking.
