OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,FIt's hoped this might break down some
OL,7,Fof the barriers women face when
OL,8,Fconsidering a political career.
OL,10,FShelaine Green, chair of the group,
OL,11,Fbelieves the programme will ensure
OL,12,Fmore "balanced decision-making in the
OL,13,FStates".
OL,15,FShe adds: "Deputies don't just bring
OL,16,Ftheir professional skills, though
OL,17,Fthose are obviously important, they
OL,18,Fbring their life experience too.
