OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,F"There's a lot of difference between a
OL,7,Fyoung female accountant and an older
OL,8,Fmale accountant - they can both sort
OL,9,Fout facts, figures, and numbers - but
OL,10,Ftheir experiences are different."
OL,12,FShelaine hopes to see more women
OL,13,Felected at the next election so that
OL,14,Fthe island's politicians better
OL,15,Funderstand the diversity of Guernsey
OL,16,Flife.
OL,18,FIn Jersey, the situation is slightly
OL,19,Fmore balanced - with 21 female to 28
OL,20,Fmale States Members.
