OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,FNonetheless, 'vote.je' hosted an
OL,7,FInternational Women's Day event on
OL,8,FSaturday 8th March, designed to
OL,9,Finspire women to engage with politics.
OL,11,FHeld in the States Chamber, women
OL,12,Fspoke to current female States Members
OL,13,Fto learn about some of the island's
OL,14,Fpolitical pioneers.
OL,16,FFor example, Ivy Forster was the first
OL,17,Ffemale deputy in Jersey, representing
OL,18,FSt Helier.
