OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,FAfter her family sheltered Russian
OL,7,Flabourers brought to the island during
OL,8,Fthe Occupation, Forster was elected to
OL,9,Fthe States Assembly in 1948.
OL,11,FEmily Thomas, the event's organiser,
OL,12,Fsays it's important for women to feel
OL,13,Fthat politics is a viable career
OL,14,Fchoice for them.
OL,16,FShe explains: "We should see an
OL,17,FAssembly that's reflective of the
OL,18,Fisland's population.
