OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,F"It's important that people see people
OL,7,Felected to make decisions about laws,
OL,8,Fabout policies in their community that
OL,9,Freflect their own community, identity,
OL,10,Fand beliefs.
OL,12,F"That's when people feel represented
OL,13,Fand heard."
OL,15,FThe event formed part of vote.je's
OL,16,Fbroader 'Plan to Stand' campaign that
OL,17,Fhopes to encourage a diverse range of
OL,18,Fcompetitive candidates to stand for
OL,19,Fthe 2026 election.
