OL,3,CHow the Channel Islands are
OL,4,Cencouraging women into politics
OL,6,FEmily adds: "If you look back at the
OL,7,F2014, 2018, and 2022 elections, there
OL,8,Fhave been more female election
OL,9,Fcandidates year on year.
OL,11,F"We can only hope that by putting on
OL,12,Fevents like this, 2026 will see
OL,13,Fanother increase again."
